{"id":306193,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/306193","type":2,"name":"半妖の夜叉姫","name_cn":"半妖的夜叉姬","summary":"永远、刹那、诸叶，是继承了妖怪与人类血脉的半妖少女们。\r\n幼时被卷入森林大火而分离的双胞胎少女，永远与刹那。永远通过能穿越时代树时空的隧道，从战国时代来到了现代。她被戈薇所在的日暮家养育长大，成长为精通武道的女初中生。与此同时，留在战国时代的妹妹刹那，在已经成为除妖师首领的琥珀手下以除妖为业。\r\n诸叶是戈薇与犬夜叉的女儿，身为赏金猎人的她拥有“妖怪杀手诸叶”这一称号，每天也是在做着除妖的工作。\r\n自从永远与刹那两人分开以来过了10年，穿越时代树时空的隧道再度开启。永远与在现代出现的刹那重逢，但刹那不知为何忘记了永远的事情。包括与刹那一同来到现代的诸叶在内，永远她们这些“半妖的夜叉姬”，开始在现代和战国时代掀起波澜。","air_date":"2020-10-03","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":166,"count":{"1":4,"2":1,"3":7,"4":13,"5":39,"6":49,"7":30,"8":18,"9":1,"10":4},"score":5.8},"rank":5006,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/84/ad/306193_cb2Hh.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/84/ad/306193_cb2Hh.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/84/ad/306193_cb2Hh.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/84/ad/306193_cb2Hh.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/84/ad/306193_cb2Hh.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":118,"collect":26,"doing":456,"on_hold":36,"dropped":111},"crt":[{"id":86133,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/86133","name":"日暮とわ","name_cn":"日暮永远","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/3a/ee/86133_crt_07qo7.jpg?r=1601775720","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/3a/ee/86133_crt_07qo7.jpg?r=1601775720","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/3a/ee/86133_crt_07qo7.jpg?r=1601775720","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3a/ee/86133_crt_07qo7.jpg?r=1601775720"},"comment":6,"collects":2,"info":{"name_cn":"日暮永远","alias":{"jp":"日暮 とわ","kana":"ひぐらし とわ","romaji":"Towa Higurashi"},"gender":"女","source":"http://hanyo-yashahime.com/character/01/"},"actors":[{"id":34048,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/34048","name":"松本沙羅","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a9/b4/34048_prsn_WNrnW.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/a9/b4/34048_prsn_WNrnW.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/a9/b4/34048_prsn_WNrnW.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a9/b4/34048_prsn_WNrnW.jpg"}}]},{"id":86134,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/8